v hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"bg-glow\"></div><div class=\"fixed inset-0 bg-noise opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none z-50 mix-blend-overlay\"></div><nav class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-40 p-4 md:p-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/10 text-white\"><a class=\"cursor-pointer flex items-center\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Proauto Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"38\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/logo.svg\"/></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex gap-12 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase items-center\"><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition-colors\" href=\"/brand\">A Marca</a><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition-colors\" href=\"/products\">Produtos</a><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contato</a><div class=\"w-px h-4 bg-white/20\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><button class=\"transition-colors px-0.5 text-accent\">PT</button></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"opacity-30\">|</span><button class=\"transition-colors px-0.5 text-white/50 hover:text-white\">EN</button></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"opacity-30\">|</span><button class=\"transition-colors px-0.5 text-white/50 hover:text-white\">ES</button></span></div></div><a class=\"mr-[30px] bg-accent text-white px-4 py-2.5 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:bg-white hover:text-ink transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\" href=\"/seja-um-revendedor\">SEJA UM REVENDEDOR</a><button class=\"flex items-center justify-center group p-2\"><svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"group-hover:text-accent transition-colors\"><line x1=\"4\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"4\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-ink text-white font-sans selection:bg-accent selection:text-ink pt-32 pb-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl\"><section class=\"mb-32 relative\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h1 class=\"font-display text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-[120px] leading-[0.85] uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8\">A MARCA<br/><span class=\"text-accent\">PROAUTO</span></h1><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">Desde 2005, redefinindo os padrões de estética automotiva no Brasil com tecnologia de ponta e paixão por performance.</p></div></section><section class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 mb-32 items-center\"><div class=\"relative h-[60vh] w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><img alt=\"Proauto Factory\" referrerPolicy=\"no-referrer\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1580273916550-e323be2ae537%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl uppercase\">Nossa História</h2><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\"><p>Nascida da paixão por carros e da busca incessante pela perfeição, a Proauto começou como um pequeno laboratório focado em desenvolver a cera perfeita.</p><p>Hoje, somos a marca líder em produtos de alta performance para estética automotiva, presentes em milhares de lares e estúdios de detalhamento profissional em todo o país.</p><p>Nossa missão é simples: fornecer os melhores produtos para que você possa cuidar do seu veículo com o mesmo nível de exigência de um profissional.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"mb-32\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl uppercase mb-16 text-center\">Nossos Pilares</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-surface p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"font-display text-6xl text-white/10 mb-6 block\">0<!-- -->1</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl uppercase mb-4\">Inovação</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">Investimento contínuo em P&amp;D para criar fórmulas exclusivas e mais eficientes.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"font-display text-6xl text-white/10 mb-6 block\">0<!-- -->2</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl uppercase mb-4\">Performance</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">Produtos testados em condições extremas para garantir resultados superiores.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"font-display text-6xl text-white/10 mb-6 block\">0<!-- -->3</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl uppercase mb-4\">Sustentabilidade</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">Compromisso com o meio ambiente através de embalagens recicláveis e fórmulas biodegradáveis.</p></div></div></section></div><section class=\"py-24 bg-surface border-y border-white/10 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 mb-16 flex justify-between items-end\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl uppercase tracking-tight\">Galeria</h2><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><button disabled=\"\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white hover:text-ink transition-colors disabled:opacity-30 disabled:hover:bg-transparent disabled:hover:text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white hover:text-ink transition-colors disabled:opacity-30 disabled:hover:bg-transpa